snippet.title: Pixels with Comics official trailer
snippet.description:
This is offical Trailer/Teaser of the Pixels With Comics Done in Unreal Engine.

Gameplay is survive, listen to musics, and try to repeat.

The story is who will rule the 2d world with destroy the others.

Genre: Indie, Musical, Bullethell.

For Wishlist Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2517210/Pixels_With_Comics/
